1. MANGA DOWNLOADER PHP CLASS VERSION 1.0

Support for: 

http://www.mangastream.com
http://www.mangareader.net
http://www.animextremist.com
http://www.submanga.com

Use your own ideas and try different loops to download more chapters at once. Have fun and enjoy :--)

2.GUIA DE USO/USE GUIDE

When you download a file its saved on the auto-created 'mangas' directory.

MANGASTREAM { English }

$obj = new mangaDownloader_ms();
//one way
$obj->download('http://mangastream.com/read/one_piece_green/59213718/1');

MANGAREADER { English }

$obj = new mangaDownloader_ar();
//two ways
$obj->download('http://www.mangareader.net/hatsukoi-limited/1');
$obj->download('http://www.mangareader.net/202-13447-1/hatsukoi-limited/chapter-1.html')

ANIMEXTREMIST { Spanish }
//una forma
$obj = new mangaDownloader_ax();
$obj->download('http://www.animextremist.com/mangas-online/naruto/capitulo-504/naruto.html');

SUBMANGA { Spanish }
//dos formas
$obj = new mangaDownloader_sm();

$obj->download('http://submanga.com/Naruto/2');
$obj->download('http://submanga.com/Naruto/2/70241')

//tambien puedes descargar el ultimo capitulo de una serie automaticamente
$obj->last('http://submanga.com/Naruto');

OTROS

Puedes configurar el demonio Cron para que ejecute un script. Mas info en la Wiki del proyecto: 
https://github.com/hcosta/mangaDownloader/wiki

